   728→
   729→    /**
   730→     * ⚠️  WARNING: DO NOT ADD NEW MIGRATIONS HERE ⚠️
   731→     *
   732→     * Schema version 42 is the FINAL version for the v1 dashboard API.
   733→     * This is due to the migration of the legacy dashboards API to the app platform.
   734→     *
   735→     * For panel-specific migrations, implement them as panel migrations in the
   736→     * individual panel plugin migration handlers instead of adding new schema versions.
   737→     */
